                ? ["Accha! Aur batao, kya chal raha hai tumhari life mein?", "Nice! Tumhe kya pasand hai karne ko? Weekend pe kya karti ho?", "Interesting! Main bhi kuch batau ya tum hi sunna chahti ho? ;)" ]
                : ["Nice! What else is going on in your life?", "Cool! What do you like to do? What are your weekends like?", "Interesting! Want to hear about me or are you just vibing? ;)"];
            } else {
