                ? ["Haan! Tumhare saath ye conversation acchi ja rahi hai. Keep going! 😊", "Accha hai! Ab aur interesting batao. Main engaged hu. 😄", "Tumhari ye baat acchi lagi! Ab zara aur batao, kya sochte ho iske baare mein?"]
                : ["Yes! This conversation is going well. Keep it coming! 😊", "Nice! Now tell me something even more interesting. I am engaged. 😄", "Love that! What else is on your mind?"];
