                ? ["Interesting! Ab ek game khelte hain - tum 3 cheezein batao apne baare mein. Ready? 😄", "Accha! Tum interesting ho. Ab meri baari hai - ready ho? ;)", "Haan! Par ab ek challenge - mujhe hasao. Go! 😊"]
